:"market"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. Its pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwqiy~uwna","text_ar":"سُوقِيُّونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", means The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"people of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suwq","text_ar":"سُوق"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 534.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adiymN suwqiY~N","text_ar":"اَدِيمٌ سُوقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A skin,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hide, prepared,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dressed; in a good state:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not prepared"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dressed:"},{"kind":"text","text":"it is ascribed to the vulgar: and there is a difference of opinion respecting it: the second [explanation, or meaning,] is that which is commonly known. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}